data.description: Come see this beautiful 5 bedroom/2bathroom completely renovated home. Renovation,  Kitchen contains marble counter tops, gas range, microwave, dish washer, breakfast bar. Seller will be leaving Stainless Steel appliances. Dining room is separate. Roof is nearly 2 years old. , A/V connections in every room, ceramics & bamboo flooring, New HVAC system, Updated electrical system. Home is equipped with outside camera and security system that Owner will be leaving.  Home is in close proximity to Downtown Macon.
